Running Event Generators with Fun4All:

### HEPGen ####
- compile and install sHEPGen.so library

- Preparing the Fun4All macro: edit Fun4All_MCEventGen.C and set:

"runpythia8 = false"
"runpythia6 = false"
"runhepgen = true"
"runsartre = false"
"readeictree = false"

root -b -q Fun4All_MCEventGen.C

### Sartre ###

to get started

add to .cshrc
 setenv SARTRE_DIR /opt/sphenix/core/stow/sartre-1.20

login in a new window
cp the sartre.cfg to working area

you will need to add the HepMC node reader after the PHSartre
to feed the hepmc node into GEANT4

for documentation on configuring Sartre, see

http://sartre.hepforge.org/


